text: Jan Káňa (born January 4, 1992) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for Olomouc HC of the Czech Extraliga. Káňa made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Kometa Brno during the 2011-12 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:Sportspeople from Zlín
